  "created_at": "2026-04-03T18:08:34.315Z",
  "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"shinobi\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"2367\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/977dab/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> shinobi:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>a basic GUI/display to pull from the logs and display to a user validation times as the blocks come in.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Here\u2019s a patch for bitcoin-tui that people might find interesting to try:</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox githubpullrequest\" data-onebox-src=\"https://github.com/janb84/bitcoin-tui/pull/25\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/janb84/bitcoin-tui/pull/25\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">github.com/janb84/bitcoin-tui</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"github-row\" data-github-private-repo=\"false\">\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"github-icon-container\" title=\"Pull Request\">\n      <svg width=\"60\" height=\"60\" class=\"github-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11 11.28V5c-.03-.78-.34-1.47-.94-2.06C9.46 2.35 8.78 2.03 8 2H7V0L4 3l3 3V4h1c.27.02.48.11.69.31.21.2.3.42.31.69v6.28A1.993 1.993 0 0 0 10 15a1.993 1.993 0 0 0 1-3.72zm-1 2.92c-.66 0-1.2-.55-1.2-1.2 0-.65.55-1.2 1.2-1.2.65 0 1.2.55 1.2 1.2 0 .65-.55 1.2-1.2 1.2zM4 3c0-1.11-.89-2-2-2a1.993 1.993 0 0 0-1 3.72v6.56A1.993 1.993 0 0 0 2 15a1.993 1.993 0 0 0 1-3.72V4.72c.59-.34 1-.98 1-1.72zm-.8 10c0 .66-.55 1.2-1.2 1.2-.65 0-1.2-.55-1.2-1.2 0-.65.55-1.2 1.2-1.2.65 0 1.2.55 1.2 1.2zM2 4.2C1.34 4.2.8 3.65.8 3c0-.65.55-1.2 1.2-1.2.65 0 1.2.55 1.2 1.2 0 .65-.55 1.2-1.2 1.2z\"></path></svg>\n    </div>\n\n  <div class=\"github-info-container\">\n\n\n\n      <h4>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/janb84/bitcoin-tui/pull/25\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Add a tab for monitoring slow blocks (#25)</a>\n      </h4>\n\n    <div class=\"branches\">\n      <code>main</code> \u2190 <code>ajtowns:202604-bip54blocks</code>\n    </div>\n\n      <div class=\"github-info\">\n        <div class=\"date\">\n          opened <span class=\"discourse-local-date\" data-format=\"ll\" data-date=\"2026-04-03\" data-time=\"18:03:13\" data-timezone=\"UTC\">06:03PM - 03 Apr 26 UTC</span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"user\">\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/ajtowns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8fdb4584494f0086a7873ac276d4821942b0737a.png\" class=\"onebox-avatar-inline\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" data-dominant-color=\"BDB7AB\">\n            ajtowns\n          </a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"lines\" title=\"3 commits changed 7 files with 1099 additions and 2 deletions\">\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/janb84/bitcoin-tui/pull/25/files\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <span class=\"added\">+1099</span>\n            <span class=\"removed\">-2</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n  <div class=\"github-row\">\n    <p class=\"github-body-container\">Probably not desirable to merge.\n\nAdds a tab for [monitoring slow blocks on si<span class=\"show-more-container\"><a href=\"https://github.com/janb84/bitcoin-tui/pull/25\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"show-more\">\u2026</a></span><span class=\"excerpt hidden\">gnet](https://delvingbitcoin.org/t/consensus-cleanup-demo-of-slow-blocks-on-signet/2367) -- displays recent blocks, when we saw the header, when we saw the block, whether it was a compact block, how long it took to validate, and if they're on a different chain than the active chain. Also tails the last few lines of the debug.log.\n\n&lt;img width=\"1074\" height=\"715\" alt=\"tui-slow-blocks\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/27319c1f-e53e-48a2-b0fc-112bd663aab6\" /&gt;</span></p>\n  </div>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>This is what a 5-block reorg looks like in it (without any of the blocks being slow):</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b4aa7b8237aa18e0cc5be06faa4d8f697f9674ab.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/b4aa7b8237aa18e0cc5be06faa4d8f697f9674ab\" title=\"tui-slow-blocks\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b4aa7b8237aa18e0cc5be06faa4d8f697f9674ab_2_690x459.png\" alt=\"tui-slow-blocks\" data-base62-sha1=\"pMfcvaF4GvFukmM5Qk0CGq4gwxJ\" width=\"690\" height=\"459\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b4aa7b8237aa18e0cc5be06faa4d8f697f9674ab_2_690x459.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b4aa7b8237aa18e0cc5be06faa4d8f697f9674ab_2_1035x688.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b4aa7b8237aa18e0cc5be06faa4d8f697f9674ab.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"1A1B19\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">tui-slow-blocks</span><span class=\"informations\">1074\u00d7715 102 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Enabling <code>-debug=cmpctblock</code> and <code>-debug=bench</code> logging are good and not very expensive and are required to fill out some of the columns; enabling <code>-debug=net</code> logging as well might also gather some interesting info.</p>",
